uint32_t pmhalTps65910RegulatorProp::voltRegAddr

The regulator voltage register address. Not all regulators have the voltage register; if not present the value of this field is expected to be NULL.

uint32_t pmhalTps65910RegulatorProp::voltSrRegAddr

The regulator SmartReflex voltage register address. Not all regulators have the SR register; if not present the value of this field is expected to be NULL.
